name: Minzy Girl - What A Day Archival Art Print (8 x 10 inches)
description:
This is a collection of Minzy Girl's series.

Missy Minzy World is a land which is filled with all sorts of mushrooms. You will bound to discover there are heaps of different mushrooms in here. The mushrooms and the other creatures in here are always in an odd & insane shape. They tend to be in all sort of beautiful colours and lovely patterns. It will always feels Oh so fantasy looking at them. The vibrant colours and whimsical illustration will sure to put a smile on your face.

This illustration was lovingly hand-drawn in ink on paper, coloured digitally and printed professionally on an archival heavyweight paper. This Giclee Print comes ready for framing measuring 8" x 10".

Please note that the colour may vary slightly then on your monitor. As computer monitors can show things a little differently with colour. Your Giclee Print will come to you very sharp and clean with NO watermark.

This lovely art will be shipped flat, in cello sleeves into a rigid envelope to protect it via Aus Post. It will be packaged and shipped with care.

The purchase of this print does not transfer reproduction rights.
Please do not use my images without permission.
All rights reserved. © Irene Andrews 2012
